      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAGIC TULHURST (2) started favourite last start at Bathurst and led from a wider barrier than this but faded to finish midfield. Recorded a string of top-four finishes prior and has the speed to push forward again from this draw so is worth another chance. CELEBRITY CRUISE (3) finished in front of MAGIC TULHURST when fourth at Bathurst last week, clocking in only 3.4m from the winner. Placed in her previous two outings, one of them at this venue when she came from the back row. Draws well so has winning claims. ROCK QUEEN (1) has been kept up to the mark with a trial since she led and fought well to go under by a nose last start at Young. She can give a big sight again from the inside draw. PEAKSART (4) has been close to the placegetters from back row draws in the last two outings. Can be competitive again returning to the front line.",
